      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the hotlines, i've seen them. but they dont actually fix the numbers. they don't make the interest stop growing or the collectors stop calling. it just feels like a cycle that never stops. like i'm just running in place while the water gets higher. it's just math at this point, and the math says i'm defeated.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
